Trend Character Choices ARGUS Posters – 13.4″ Width x 19″ Height – Assorted Motivational posters feature lively visuals and popular themes to energize learning, spark discussions, build character, and encourage new ways of looking at life. The results are motivated, successful students who reflect the positive attitudes and behaviors portrayed in these creative themes. Six-poster set includes Trustworthiness, Caring, Respect, Citizenship, Fairness, and Responsibility. Posters are durable for classroom posting.
